    <name>XL Converter</name>
    <summary>Convert images</summary>
    <description>
        <p>XL Converter is an easy-to-use image converter for modern formats.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Batch transcode images to JPEG XL, AVIF, WebP, JPEG and PNG.</li>
            <li>Encode better quality JPEG images with JPEGLI.</li>
            <li>Losslessly recompress your JPEG images.</li>
            <li>Convert faster with parallel encoding.</li>
            <li>Scale down images and preserve metadata with ExifTool.</li>
            <li>QoL features available: drag 'n drop, dark theme, keep directory structure, copy smaller sources, and many more!</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    <launchable type="desktop-id">eu.codepoems.xl-converter.desktop</launchable>
